## @paalstack/react-icons

Always import from the specific family sub-path. Never from root.

```tsx
// ✅ Correct — import from sub-path
import { LuSettings, LuUser, LuSearch, LuMoon, LuSun } from '@paalstack/react-icons/lu'; // Lucide (preferred)
import { HiMoon } from '@paalstack/react-icons/hi2';
import { FaGithub } from '@paalstack/react-icons/fa6';

// ❌ Wrong
import { LuUser } from '@paalstack/react-icons';

// Usage
<LuSettings className="size-5 text-muted-foreground" />
<Button variant="outline" size="sm"><LuMoon className="mr-2 size-4" />Dark mode</Button>
import { IconButton } from '@paalstack/react-ui';
<IconButton aria-label="Settings" icon={<LuSettings className="size-5" />} />
```

Available families: `/lu` (Lucide — default) · `/hi2` · `/fa6` · `/tb` · `/md` · `/ri` · `/bi` · `/bs` · `/fi` · `/io5` · `/rx` · `/si` · `/pi` · `/vsc` · `/go`

